truecrypt (7.1a-9) xenial; urgency=medium

  * Fix "Invalid characters encountered" error when mounting that started happening in 16.04.
  * Use xdg-open as fallback when opening directories.
  * The "User's Guide" menu item now works.
  * Updated help items to community websites that have more useful info than the discontinued notice on truecrypt.org.

 -- Stefan Sundin <stefan@stefansundin.com>  Sat, 23 Apr 2016 22:19:18 -0700

truecrypt (7.1a-8) vivid; urgency=low

  * TrueCrypt is now automatically added to your Startup Applications.
  * New indicator icon that looks way better.
  * Removed options in the preferences that had no effect on the indicator menu.
  * Changed default of "Exit when there are no mounted volumes" to false.

 -- Stefan Sundin <stefan@stefansundin.com>  Thu, 23 Apr 2015 23:55:37 -0700

